---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Technical & AV">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Technical & AV</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Technical execution across live sound, AV systems, international congress environments,
      and visual post-production.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section text">
    <h2>Sound & AV Operations</h2>
    <p>
      Live sound and AV support for events and professional environments, combining hands-on operation with tech-host coordination, with a focus on
      reliability, clear communication, and calm execution under pressure.
      
    </p>
    
    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>Live sound, AV systems support, and troubleshooting</li>
      <li>International congress / conference environments (hybrid: tech host + hands-on AV)</li>

    </ul>
    <p class="muted">
      Experience includes congress work starting in 2022 (Pavilhão do Conhecimento, PT) and major events in Denmark, France, Spain, and Germany.
    </p>
    
  </section>

  <section class="section text">
    <h2>Image Editing & Post-Production</h2>
    <p>
      Advanced image editing for promotional and production contexts, ranging from
clean restoration to complex compositing.

    </p>
    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>Flyers and compositing (layered design, integration, refinement)</li>
      <li>Restoration and cleanup (damage repair, artifact removal)</li>
      <li>AI upscale and enhancement (detail recovery, noise and compression cleanup)</li>
      <li>Artist promos (visual consistency, finishing and polish)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="muted">
      Proof will be added as before/after examples and a small curated selection of final visuals.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section text">
    <h2>Video Editing</h2>
    <p>
      Video editing for promo, event documentation, and multimedia work. Focused on pacing,
      clarity, and delivery-ready outputs.
    </p>
    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>Promo edits and short-form content</li>
      <li>Event and conference edits</li>
      <li>Cleanup and visual refinement where needed</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="section text">
    <h2>Selected Video Work</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      A small curated selection of edits and technical/media work.
    </p>
  
    <div class="video-grid">
      <div class="video-card">
        <div class="video-frame ratio-9x16">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hvkrD2EP2ms"
            title="Short-form edit"
