  </section>
  
  <section class="section text">
    <h2>Training</h2>
    <p>
      Sound Technician course completed in 2024 (Soundbooking Portugal), reinforcing
professional standards for live and production environments.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <p class="muted">
      If you’re booking for a festival, congress, or production context, use the Contact page and
